text: The office had a small reception which usually is vacant. The project they are handling is Astro. The call floor is quite long and open. Publicity isn't too much, so it is hard to look for contact information online for the Nusajaya branch. The location of the building is at a condominium, so it would really be a plus point if you are staying there and working in Brandt International as you could save on travelling time and cost.
